        <type>float</type>
        <definition>float MLMeshingSettings::fill_hole_length</definition>
        <argsstring></argsstring>
        <name>fill_hole_length</name>
        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Any hole which has perimeter (in meters) less than fill_hole_length will be filled. The maximum hole perimeter is limited to 5 meters. Also The maximum area of the hole should not exceed 0.5 square meters. If the hole overlaps with neighboring mesh block/s, it won&apos;t be filled in. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
